Class Database

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oose2015.grapevine.Database

  • public class Database
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a dummy database created so that we could perform basic tests. Created by venussoontornprueksa on 10/23/15. This may become our service for sending data between front- and back-end.
